        @Deprecated
public void setMessageConverter(MessageConverter messageConverter)
        Deprecated. - this converter is not used by the container; it was only used to configure the converter for a @RabbitListener adapter. That is now handled differently. If you are manually creating a listener container, the converter must be configured in a listener adapter (if present).
        Set the MessageConverter strategy for converting AMQP Messages.
        Parameters:
        messageConverter - the message converter to use
